        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued July 18 at 1:13PM MDT by NWS Pueblo CO</headline>
        <description>At 112 PM MDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm 13
miles northwest of La Garita, or 45 miles northwest of Alamosa,
moving east at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts up to 50 mph and pea size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects. Minor hail damage to vegetation is
possible.

Locations impacted include...
La Garita.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
